{% extends 'layouts/default.j2' %}
{% block content %}
	<p>Hi I'm Antoine, welcome to my website. I'm always exploring IT ideas about projects that could make people's live more private and secure. Besides that, I...</p>
	<ul>
		<li>like to learn languages, I speak some french, python, english, js, spanish... ;</li>
